==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bird fancier
<hw>Bird" fan`ci*er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who takes
pleasure in rearing or collecting rare or curious birds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who has for sale the various kinds of birds
which are kept in cages.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Birdie</ent>⟦br⟧
